msgid "Restrict keys"
msgstr "Begränsa nycklar"

#: booking/metadata_forms.py:47
msgid "Check to restrict the door to the Lounge to only open with your key"
msgstr ""
"Kryssa i för att begränsa Loungens dörr att endast öppnas med din nyckel"

#: booking/metadata_forms.py:51 booking/metadata_forms.py:94
msgid "Doorcode"
msgstr "Dörrkod"

#: booking/metadata_forms.py:52
msgid ""
"Optionally provide a doorcode with which the door to the Lounge can be "
"opened during your booking"
msgstr ""
"Vid behov, ange en dörrkod med vilken dörren till Loungen kan öppnas under "
"din bokning"

